    innerHTML:
      ' <p align="justify"><span><b>(1) </b>Every pipe that passes through an exterior wall to supply water to the exterior of the <i>building</i> shall be provided with,</span></p> <p align="justify"><span>(a) a frost-proof hydrant with a separate shut-off valve located inside the <i>building</i>, or</span></p> <p align="justify"><span>(b) a stop-and-waste cock located inside the <i>building</i> and close to the wall.</span></p> <p align="justify"><span ',
