    innerHTML:
      ' <p align="justify"><span><b>(1) </b>Except as permitted in Article 9.10.9.3., a wall or floor assembly required to be a <i>fire separation</i> shall be constructed as a continuous barrier against the spread of fire.</span></p> <p align="justify"><span><b>(2) </b>The continuity of a <i>fire separation</i> shall be maintained where it abuts another <i>fire separation</i>, a floor, a ceiling, a roof or an exterior wall assembly.</span></p> <p align="justify"><span ',
